---
// Subtle CRT scanline + vignette overlay (perf-light, pointer-events none)
---
<div class="crt-overlay" aria-hidden="true"></div>
<style>
  .crt-overlay { position:fixed; inset:0; z-index:25; pointer-events:none; mix-blend-mode:overlay; }
  .crt-overlay::before, .crt-overlay::after { content:""; position:absolute; inset:0; }
  /* Scanlines */
  .crt-overlay::before { background:repeating-linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(0,0,0,0.15) 0 1px, transparent 1px 3px); opacity:.28; }
  /* Vignette */
  .crt-overlay::after { background:radial-gradient(circle at 50% 50%, rgba(0,0,0,0) 55%, rgba(0,0,0,0.35)); mix-blend-mode:multiply; }
  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce){ .crt-overlay{ display:none; } }
</style>